收受送達後五日內向本院提出抗告狀。\r\n                                    書記官  徐仁豐\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　3 　　月　　17　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/110%2c%e8%81%b2%2c976%2c20210317%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,110,聲,976,20210317,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"976","JDATE":"20210317","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}